c/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=678&amp;height=452&amp;aspect_ratio=678:452 1x, https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=1356&amp;height=904&amp;aspect_ratio=1356:904 2x"><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=548&amp;height=365&amp;aspect_ratio=548:365 1x, https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=1096&amp;height=730&amp;aspect_ratio=1096:730 2x"><source media="(min-width: 768px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=478&amp;height=318&amp;aspect_ratio=478:318 1x, https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=956&amp;height=636&amp;aspect_ratio=956:636 2x"><source media="(min-width: 640px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=669&amp;height=446&amp;aspect_ratio=669:446 1x, https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=1338&amp;height=892&amp;aspect_ratio=1338:892 2x"><!--]--><img onerror="this.setAttribute(&#39;data-error&#39;, 1)" width="557" height="371" alt="Duotone_Kiteboarding_Dice-SLS_Action-Shots_9" loading="lazy" data-nuxt-img data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=557&amp;height=371&amp;aspect_ratio=557:371 1x, https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=1114&amp;height=742&amp;aspect_ratio=1114:742 2x" title class="media-slide__image lazyload" src="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/68ae/c0cc/59f1/b319/1fdf/5b82/original/Website-DTK-Duotone-WhipD-LAB-TrustBar-MatchuLopes-TobyBromwich-7571.jpg?width=557&amp;height=371&amp;aspect_ratio=557:371"></picture><div class="media-slide__content"><!--[--><!--]--></div></div></div><!--]--></li><!--]--><!--]--></ul></div><!--]--></div><!--]--></div></div><!--]--></div><!--[--><!--]--></div></div><div id="description" style="scroll-margin-top:50px;" class="container-section product-description" _uid="8be339b2-b504-4773-8ebb-82596b8acab8" component="ProductDescription" product-title="Dice SLS" price-threshold="100"><div class="container"><!----><!--[--><div class="product-description__container"><div class="product-description__headline"><h4 class="h4">The Duotone Dice SLS 2026 is a sporty freestyle and wave allrounder designed for advanced riders. With its innovative materials and superior performance characteristics, it offers pure control, explosive pop, and exceptional stability across a variety of conditions. </h4></div><div class="product-description__body"><div class="richtext"><span></span><div class="richtext--clamped richtext__text-container">The Duotone Dice SLS, the ultimate sporty freestyle and wave allrounder crafted for advanced riders. Built with premium Penta TX and Trinity TX materials, the Dice SLS offers pure and intuitive control on three struts, providing an exhilarating experience whether you’re performing technical tricks or riding the waves. <br /><br />This kite is designed for those who demand explosive pop and crisp slack in their freestyle maneuvers. Spicy it up and experience effortless drift while navigating waves, allowing you to maintain speed and control as you harness the energy of the ocean. With smooth and balanced power, the Dice SLS delivers the kind of performance that inspires confidence in any session. The Dice SLS features speedy turning capabilities, making it a solid performer in all conditions. One of the key advancements is the longer depower stroke, which enables smoother power delivery. The refined arc shape, with a more open center and aggressively pulled-in tips, enhances the depower range while maintaining progressive power development for smooth transitions. Lighter steering is achieved through improvements to the canopy tension and attachment at the tip. This enhances the transfer of steering input, resulting in reduced bar pressure without compromising feedback, giving riders a more engaging experience on the water. Faster and more controlled turning is another highlight of the Dice SLS. With adjusted batten positions and an improved canopy structure, tip flutter is minimized, allowing for tighter, quicker, and more precise turns— essential for both loops and tight maneuvers. When it comes to wave riding, the Dice SLS offers playful and reactive handling. Enhanced steering responsiveness and balanced power delivery make it lively and easier to maneuver in dynamic wave conditions, allowing riders to carve through the surf with ease. Moreover, the optimized bridle setup and improved load distribution provide increased control in gusty or challenging conditions, ensuring stability when faced with unpredictable winds. To top it off, the Dice SLS has been fine-tuned for freestyle performance. A deeper position in the wind window, combined with a refined shape, delivers explosive pop and clean slack, making it easier to execute hooked or unhooked technical tricks with confidence. <br /><br />Challenge yourself with the Duotone Dice SLS 2026, the perfect combination of performance, versatility, and cutting-edge technology for those ambitious riders who thrive in both freestyle and wave riding scenarios. </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!--]--></div><!--[--><!--]--></div><div style="scroll-margin-top:50px;" class="container-section" _uid="359c9a6e-7a90-4244-b099-e616788b1a75" component="ProductKeyFeaturesPerformanceSizesGroup" product-title="Dice SLS" price-threshold="100"><div class="container"><!----><!--[--><div class="collapsible" id="key-features"><!----><button class="collapsible__button"><h2 class="collapsible__label">Key Features</h2><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true" role="img" class="icon collapsible__minus" style="" width="24px" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-v-ac1ff433><path fill="currentColor" d="M8.12 14.71L12 10.83l3.88 3.88a.996.996 0 1 0 1.41-1.41L12.7 8.71a.996.996 0 0 0-1.41 0L6.7 13.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41c.39.38 1.03.39 1.42 0"/></svg></button><div class="collapsible-container collapsible-container--active"><div class="collapsible-container__content--active collapsible-container__content"><!--[--><div class="collapsible__container"><!--[--><div class="keyfeatures"><div class="keyfeatures__cols_3 keyfeatures__grid"><!--[--><div class="description"><div class="description__headline">The Sporty Freestyle &amp; Wave Allrounder </div><div class="richtext description__rich-text"><span></span><div class="richtext__text-container">The Dice SLS blends explosive freestyle performance with fast, responsive wave handling—perfect for riders who demand versatility without compromise. </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="description"><div class="description__headline">Explosive Pop and Crisp Slack </div><div class="richtext description__rich-text"><span></span><div class="richtext__text-container">Tuned for freestyle performance, delivering strong takeoff power and clean slack to support advanced unhooked tricks with precision and confidence.  </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="description"><div class="description__headline">Smooth and Balanced Power </div><div class="richtext description__rich-text"><span></span><div class="richtext__text-container">The Dice SLS delivers steady, predictable pull across a wide wind range—ensuring comfort, control, and confidence in any session. </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="description"><div class="description__headline">Effortless Drift in Waves </div><div class="richtext description__rich-text"><span></span><div class="richtext__text-container">Thanks to its responsive turning and well-balanced power delivery, the kite drifts naturally down the line, making it easy to stay in position on the wave. </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="description"><div class="description__headline">Pure and Intuitive Control </div><div class="richtext description__rich-text"><span></span><div class="richtext__text-container">Its balanced structure and tuned bar feedback create a direct connection between rider and kite, delivering precise, natural handling from the very first session. </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="description"><div class="description__headline">Speedy Turning </div><div class="richtext description__rich-text"><span></span><div class="richtext__text-container">Fast and precise steering lets you loop, carve, or redirect the kite exactly when needed, without feeling nervous or overly aggressive. </div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!--]--></div></div><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--></div><!--]--></div></div></div><div class="collapsible" id="performance"><!----><button class="collapsible__button"><h2 class="collapsible__label">Performance</h2><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true" role="img" class="icon collapsible__minus" style="" width="24px" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-v-ac1ff433><path fill="currentColor" d="M8.12 14.71L12 10.83l3.88 3.88a.996.996 0 1 0 1.41-1.41L12.7 8.71a.996.996 0 0 0-1.41 0L6.7 13.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41c.39.38 1.03.39 1.42 0"/></svg></button><div class="collapsible-container collapsible-container--active"><div class="collapsible-container__content--active collapsible-container__content"><!--[--><div class="collapsible__container"><!--[--><div class="performance grid"><div class="col-12 col-lg-4 performance__media"><picture class="responsive-image"><!--[--><source media="(min-width: 1440px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?width=840&amp;height=840&amp;aspect_ratio=840:840"><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?width=600&amp;height=600&amp;aspect_ratio=600:600"><source media="(min-width: 768px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?width=1440&amp;height=1440&amp;aspect_ratio=1440:1440"><source media="(min-width: 640px)" data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?width=1200&amp;height=1200&amp;aspect_ratio=1200:1200"><!--]--><img onerror="this.setAttribute(&#39;data-error&#39;, 1)" width="350" height="350" alt="Dice SLS - C01:undyed/turquoise" loading="lazy" data-nuxt-img data-srcset="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?width=700&amp;height=700&amp;aspect_ratio=700:700" title class="responsive-image--default lazyload" src="https://www.duotonesports.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?width=350&amp;height=350&amp;aspect_ratio=350:350"></picture></div><div class="col-12 col-lg-8"><div class="performance__container"><div class="performance__grid"><!--[--><!--[--><div class="performance-item"><div class="performance-item__title">Freestyle Unhooked</div><div class="performance-item__subtitle">SLACK / POP</div><div class="performance-item__value-meter"><div class="performance-item__bar"><div class="performance-item__value" style="width:0%;"></div></div><div class="performance-item__value-label" style="left:0%;"></div></div></div><div class="performance-item"><div class="performance-item__title">Freestyle Hooked</div><div class="performance-item__subtitle">KITELOOP / BIG AIR / HANGTIME</div><div class="performance-item__value-meter"><div class="performance-item__bar"><div class="performance-item__value" style="width:0%;"></div></div><div class="performance-item__value-label" style="left:0%;"></div></div></div><div class="performance-item"><div class="performance-item__title">Freeride</div><div class="performance-item__subtitle">WINDRANGE / UP WIND / SHEET &amp; GO</div><div class="performance-item__value-meter"><div class="performance-item__bar"><div class="performance-item__value" style="width:0%;"></div></div><div class="performance-item__value-label" style="left:0%;"></div></div></div><div class="performance-item"><div class="performance-item__title">Foil</div><div class="performance-item__subtitle">FLYING ABILITY IN LIGHTWIND</div><div class="performance-item__value-meter"><div class="performance-item__bar"><div class="performance-item__value" style="width:0%;"></div></div><div class="performance-item__value-label" style="left:0%;"></div></div></div><div class="performance-item"><div class="performance-item__title">Wave</div><div class="performance-item__subtitle">DRIFT / TURNING DEPOWERED / FAST TURNING</div><div class="performance-item__value-meter"><div class="performance-item__bar"><div class="performance-item__value" style="width:0%;"></div></div><div class="performance-item__value-label" style="left:0%;"></div></div></div><div class="performance-item"><div class="performance-item__title">Entry</div><div class="performance-item__subtitle">EASY RELAUNCH ABILITY / STABILITY IN AIR</div><div class="performance-item__value-meter"><div class="performance-item__bar"><div class="performance-item__value" style="width:0%;"></div></div><div class="performance-item__value-label" style="left:0%;"></div></div></div><!--]--><!--]--></div></div></div></div><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--></div><!--]--></div></div></div><div class="collapsible" id="sizesAndSpecs" style="scroll-margin-top:280px;"><div class="collapsible__left-fluid-block"></div><button class="collapsible__button"><h2 class="collapsible__label">Sizes and Specs</h2><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true" role="img" class="icon collapsible__minus" style="" width="24px" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-v-ac1ff433><path fill="currentColor" d="M8.12 14.71L12 10.83l3.88 3.88a.996.996 0 1 0 1.41-1.41L12.7 8.71a.996.996 0 0 0-1.41 0L6.7 13.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41c.39.38 1.03.39 1.42 0"/></svg></button><div class="collapsible-container collapsible-container--overflow-x collapsible-container--active"><div class="collapsible-container__content--active collapsible-container__content"><!--[--><div class="collapsible__container"><!--[--><div class="product-sizes-and-specs"><div class="scrollable-table size-finder-table"><div class=""><div class="pagination-container swiper__pagination"><!--[--><button><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink