0-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2599,"language":2600,"handle":8,"iso":2601,"lang":2600,"path":2602},"br","pt","pt-br","/pt/br/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2604,"language":2591,"handle":8,"iso":2591,"lang":2591,"path":2605},"global","/fr/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2604,"language":2595,"handle":8,"iso":2595,"lang":2595,"path":2607},"/de/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2604,"language":2587,"handle":8,"iso":2587,"lang":2587,"path":2609},"/it/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2604,"language":2611,"handle":8,"iso":2611,"lang":2611,"path":2612},"es","/es/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2604,"language":2614,"handle":8,"iso":2614,"lang":2615,"path":2616},"en","default","/en/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2618,"language":2614,"handle":8,"iso":2619,"lang":2615,"path":2620},"uk","en-uk","/en/uk/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2586,"language":2614,"handle":8,"iso":2622,"lang":2615,"path":2623},"en-ch","/en/ch/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2625,"language":2614,"handle":8,"iso":2626,"lang":2615,"path":2627},"us","en-us","/en/us/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"articleNumber":9,"region":2599,"language":2614,"handle":8,"iso":2629,"lang":2615,"path":2630},"en-br","/en/br/products/duotone-dice-sls-2026-44260-3012",{"brand":5,"articleNumber":9,"shopifyId":2632,"category":6,"flags":2633,"webname":2634,"handle":8,"colors":2635,"subline":2641,"sizeCharts":2642,"description":2643,"descriptionShort":2644,"wetsuitTemperatures":463,"keyFeatures":2645,"harnessSpecs":463,"materials":463,"sustainabilityFeatures":2664,"metaTitle":2665,"metaDescription":2666,"fromPrice":2667,"variants":2668,"vendor":2940,"vendorLine":7,"productQuotes":2941,"productTests":2954,"videos":2955,"actionShots":2960,"relatedProducts":3015,"iconFeatures":3019,"lookbooks":3020,"isClimateNeutral":271,"emersyaUrl":3021,"sizeMin":2672,"sizeMax":2907,"attachments":3022,"featureTableMatrix":3023,"featureTableSizeFinder":3068,"styleFinder":3187,"styleFinderPdp":3216,"techFeature":3223,"productProfile":463,"buyboxVideos":3236,"construction":3237,"fitGuideIcons":463,"productHotspotPictures":3238,"commonCategory":6,"genders":3261,"modelInfo":3262,"reviews":3263,"isBladderSparepart":271,"orderInfo":463,"properties":3274,"collectionId":22,"preOrderVip":271,"isMtoBoard":271,"faqs":3306},"gid://shopify/Product/15352697454979",[],"Dice SLS",[2636,2637,2638,2639,2640],"C01:undyed/turquoise","C02:sand/purple","C03:dark-grey/pink","C04:pink/dark-grey","C06:green/heron","FREESTYLE / WAVE",[],"The Duotone Dice SLS, the ultimate sporty freestyle and wave allrounder crafted for advanced riders. Built with premium Penta TX and Trinity TX materials, the Dice SLS offers pure and intuitive control on three struts, providing an exhilarating experience whether you’re performing technical tricks or riding the waves. \n\nThis kite is designed for those who demand explosive pop and crisp slack in their freestyle maneuvers. Spicy it up and experience effortless drift while navigating waves, allowing you to maintain speed and control as you harness the energy of the ocean. With smooth and balanced power, the Dice SLS delivers the kind of performance that inspires confidence in any session. The Dice SLS features speedy turning capabilities, making it a solid performer in all conditions. One of the key advancements is the longer depower stroke, which enables smoother power delivery. The refined arc shape, with a more open center and aggressively pulled-in tips, enhances the depower range while maintaining progressive power development for smooth transitions. Lighter steering is achieved through improvements to the canopy tension and attachment at the tip. This enhances the transfer of steering input, resulting in reduced bar pressure without compromising feedback, giving riders a more engaging experience on the water. Faster and more controlled turning is another highlight of the Dice SLS. With adjusted batten positions and an improved canopy structure, tip flutter is minimized, allowing for tighter, quicker, and more precise turns— essential for both loops and tight maneuvers. When it comes to wave riding, the Dice SLS offers playful and reactive handling. Enhanced steering responsiveness and balanced power delivery make it lively and easier to maneuver in dynamic wave conditions, allowing riders to carve through the surf with ease. Moreover, the optimized bridle setup and improved load distribution provide increased control in gusty or challenging conditions, ensuring stability when faced with unpredictable winds. To top it off, the Dice SLS has been fine-tuned for freestyle performance. A deeper position in the wind window, combined with a refined shape, delivers explosive pop and clean slack, making it easier to execute hooked or unhooked technical tricks with confidence. \n\nChallenge yourself with the Duotone Dice SLS 2026, the perfect combination of performance, versatility, and cutting-edge technology for those ambitious riders who thrive in both freestyle and wave riding scenarios. ","The Duotone Dice SLS 2026 is a sporty freestyle and wave allrounder designed for advanced riders. With its innovative materials and superior performance characteristics, it offers pure control, explosive pop, and exceptional stability across a variety of conditions. ",[2646,2649,2652,2655,2658,2661],{"headline":2647,"text":2648,"image":463},"The Sporty Freestyle & Wave Allrounder ","The Dice SLS blends explosive freestyle performance with fast, responsive wave handling—perfect for riders who demand versatility without compromise. ",{"headline":2650,"text":2651,"image":463},"Explosive Pop and Crisp Slack ","Tuned for freestyle performance, delivering strong takeoff power and clean slack to support advanced unhooked tricks with precision and confidence.  ",{"headline":2653,"text":2654,"image":463},"Smooth and Balanced Power ","The Dice SLS delivers steady, predictable pull across a wide wind range—ensuring comfort, control, and confidence in any session. ",{"headline":2656,"text":2657,"image":463},"Effortless Drift in Waves ","Thanks to its responsive turning and well-balanced power delivery, the kite drifts naturally down the line, making it easy to stay in position on the wave. ",{"headline":2659,"text":2660,"image":463},"Pure and Intuitive Control ","Its balanced structure and tuned bar feedback create a direct connection between rider and kite, delivering precise, natural handling from the very first session. ",{"headline":2662,"text":2663,"image":463},"Speedy Turning ","Fast and precise steering lets you loop, carve, or redirect the kite exactly when needed, without feeling nervous or overly aggressive. ",[],"Duotone Dice SLS 2026 | The Ultimate Freestyle and Wave Allrounder","Experience the Duotone Dice SLS 2026: designed for advanced riders, it offers intuitive control and explosive performance. Perfect for freestyle and waves, for unforgettable sessions.",1829,[2669,2715,2741,2781,2808,2844,2869,2904],{"id":2670,"brand":5,"articleNumber":9,"price":2671,"color":2636,"size":2672,"variantId":2673,"image":2674,"link":2678,"d2c":41,"availableForSale":41,"showNotifyOnRestock":271,"pictures":2679,"sizes":2696,"unavailableSizes":2698,"shopifyVariantId":2699,"currencyCode":2700,"continueSellingWhenOutOfStock":271,"followUpProducts":2701,"deliveryDate":2702,"webname":2634,"matchingVariants":2703,"ean":2713,"title":2714,"category":6,"preOrderVip":271,"description":2643},"67a4567d8ea4cb00064a7c63","1829.0","06.0","56322338128259",{"filename":2675,"alt":2676,"provider":2677},"https://cdn.boards-and-more.com/system/product_picture_gallery_pictures/files/6836/c3a8/44c3/2d01/2b49/7cca/original/DICE26_SLS_CC01_-_PP1.png?1748419456