dRange":3074,"weight":3089,"size":3120},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3077,"size":3112},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3078,"size":3112},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3079,"size":3112},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3080,"size":3112},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3081,"size":3112},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3082,"size":3112},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3083,"size":3148},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3084,"size":3148},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3085,"size":3131},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3086,"size":3131},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3087,"size":3183},"8:7:N/A",{"windRange":3075,"weight":3088,"size":3134},{"windRange":3075,"weight":3089,"size":3186},"9:7:6",[3188,3194,3198,3203,3208,3213],{"name":3189,"label":3190,"description":3191,"value":3192,"valueType":3193},"freestyle_unhooked","Freestyle Unhooked","SLACK / POP",18,"integer",{"name":3195,"label":3196,"description":3197,"value":3192,"valueType":3193},"freestyle_hooked","Freestyle Hooked","KITELOOP / BIG AIR / HANGTIME",{"name":3199,"label":3200,"description":3201,"value":3202,"valueType":3193},"freeride","Freeride","WINDRANGE / UP WIND / SHEET & GO",13,{"name":3204,"label":3205,"description":3206,"value":3207,"valueType":3193},"foil","Foil","FLYING ABILITY IN LIGHTWIND",12,{"name":3209,"label":3210,"description":3211,"value":3212,"valueType":3193},"wave","Wave","DRIFT / TURNING DEPOWERED / FAST TURNING",15,{"name":948,"label":946,"description":3214,"value":3215,"valueType":3193},"EASY RELAUNCH ABILITY / STABILITY IN AIR",10,[3217,3218,3219,3220,3221,3222],{"name":3189,"label":3190,"description":3191,"value":3192,"valueType":3193},{"name":3195,"label":3196,"description":3197,"value":3192,"valueType":3193},{"name":3199,"label":3200,"description":3201,"value":3202,"valueType":3193},{"name":3204,"label":3205,"description":3206,"value":3207,"valueType":3193},{"name":3209,"label":3210,"description":3211,"value":3212,"valueType":3193},{"name":948,"label":946,"description":3214,"value":3215,"valueType":3193},[3224,3227,3230,3233],{"title":3225,"description":3226},"Anti Snag","\u003Cp>The Anti Snag webbing is preventing the lines from tangling around the tip of the kite. Waterstarts are made easier and safety is increased.\u003C/p>",{"title":3228,"description":3229},"Trinity TX","\u003Cp>Teijin is the world’s leading supplier of polyester fabrics and sail materials to marine sports. The combined creative power of Duotone Kiteboarding saw the formulation of TRINITY TX. Exclusive to Duotone Kiteboarding, TRINITY TX is a 3x2 canopy material, which has proven to be far superior to other canopy materials in terms of durability and dynamic performance. The 3x2 yarn combination has proven to be the best solution in performance as well as durability, overall superior to any 2x2 or 4x4 yarn solutions. TRINITY TX. Made to stand the test of time.\u003C/p>",{"title":3231,"description":3232},"Penta TX Frame Construction","\u003Cp>Penta TX, the guarantee for a more sporty, more precise and crisp feel of the kite, achieved by 15% less overall weight and a five times higher tear resistance. Penta TX replaces Dacron and is showing 50% less elongation compared to standard Dacron. Penta T is a quite stiff material, resulting in a high structural stiffness, especially recognizable in strong wind conditions, leading to less deformation of the overall structure of the kite. It's responsible for a very precise timing when edging, releasing the edge and all steering impulses - the precise and reliable steering of a racing car. Penta TX is used in the leading edge and the center strut.\u003C/p>",{"title":3234,"description":3235},"Kook Proof Connectors","\u003Cp>The kook proof line connection points prevent accidents by guaranteeing that you cannot accidentally connect your lines incorrectly when rigging your kite.\u003C/p>",[],{"commonValue":654,"value":654},{"aspectRatio":3239,"image":3240,"hotspots":3243},"1.0:1",{"filename":3241,"alt":3242,"provider":2677},"https://cdn.boards-and-more.com/system/product_hotspot_pictures/pict